Add authentication and system-admin authorization to each KSS action. Either:

1. Create an authenticated action client variant:
```typescript
export const adminActionClient = actionClientWithMeta.use(async ({ next }) => {
  const user = await getUserOrThrow();
  if (!isSystemAdmin(user.email)) {
    throw new Error('Unauthorized: system admin required');
  }
  return next({ ctx: { user } });
});
```

2. Or add `getUserOrThrow()` + `isSystemAdmin` checks inside each action handler before performing mutations.

